查斯特·贝宁顿的儿子表示，自从他分享了对林肯公园乐队的批评以来，林肯公园的粉丝们一直对他“咄咄逼人” https://www.nme.com/news/music/chester-benningtons-son-says-linkin-park-fans-have-been-aggressive-towards-him-since-he-shared-criticism-of-the- band-3792624?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chester-benningtons-son-says-linkin-park-fans-自从他分享了乐队的批评以来就一直对他有攻击性Tom SkinnerWed, 11 Sep 2024 10:19:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3792624 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="海梅·本宁顿" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “[乐队]没有来找我宣布这个消息，他们没有问我感觉如何”</p><p>查斯特·贝宁顿 (Chester Bennington) 的儿子在帖子中表示，自从他在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chester-benningtons-son-says-linkin-park-fans-have-been-aggressive-towards-him-since-he-shared-criticism-of-the-band-3792624">发表对林肯公园乐队的批评以来，粉丝们一直对他表现出“攻击性”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="海梅·本宁顿" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/JaimeBennington-Linkin-Park-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chester-bennington">查斯特·贝宁顿</a>的儿子声称，自从他批评乐队的新版本以来<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">，林肯公园的</a>粉丝一直对他“咄咄逼人”。</p><p>上周四（9 月 5 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">，该乐队在一场直播活动中宣布回归</a>，并邀请前 Dead Sara 成员 Emily Armstrong 作为新歌手首次亮相。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/linkin-park-new-singer-emily-armstrong-chester-bennington-from-zero-3791172">“这不是结束，这不是开始”：林肯公园以新面孔展望未来</a></strong></li></ul><p>在此<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-parks-mysterious-countdown-clock-ends-and-then-begins-counting-up-again-3788436">之前，林肯公园与粉丝发布了神秘的倒计时消息，</a>引发了数周的猜测。他们的惊喜回归让他们表演了一首名为“The Emptiness Machine”的新歌和一些林肯公园的经典歌曲， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">宣布了一张名为“From Zero”的新专辑，并分享了世界巡演的细节</a>。</p><p>阿姆斯特朗作为前主唱本宁顿的替代者加入了阵容，<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/chester-bennington-obituary-1976-2017-2113700">后者于 2017 年自杀身亡</a>。</p><p>艺术家和粉丝们对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-artists-react-to-new-linkin-park-singer-emily-armstrong-3791263">林肯公园的新配置的最初反应基本上是积极的</a>。然而，阿姆斯特朗似乎与山达基教和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/danny-masterson-sentenced-to-30-years-to-life-in-prison-for-rape-3494826">被定罪的强奸犯丹尼·马斯特森</a>有联系后，很快就引起了争议。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mars-volta">The Mars Volta</a>和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/at-the-drive-in">At The Drive-In</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-fans-re-share-cedric-bixler-zavalas-message-to-emily-armstrong-over-alleged-links-to-scientology-and-danny-masterson-3791311">塞德里克·比克斯勒-萨瓦拉 (Cedric Bixler-Zavala) 向这位歌手发送的消息被转发</a>后，这一消息被曝光。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chester-benningtons-son-jaime-hits-out-at-mike-shinoda-for-betraying-trust-of-linkin-park-fans-with-emily-armstrong-3791931">本宁顿 28 岁的儿子杰米后来猛烈抨击了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-shinoda">迈克·筱田</a>的言论。后者解释说，歌迷可能需要“时间来思考”乐队与阿姆斯特朗的重组。他还表示，那些因这一决定而“不尊重”他的人将“反过来失去我的尊重”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_l3pbhS-BE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560